<div id="review_3928930366" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3928930366" />
    <a title="Cal" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/128724478-cal"><img alt="Cal" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1635564434p2/128724478.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3928930366?book_show_action=true">Apr 10, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cal" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cal" href="/user/show/128724478-cal">Cal</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3928930366" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6856227003706250577">This book was amazing! The writing style improved and I began to closely relate more with Hunter, who&apos;s now a teenager. I really enjoyed witnessing how Hunter becomes more and more conscious of his surrounding. His character development was exceptional and even I am learning from his experiences and from the way he faces the not-so-normal challenges around him. Plot wise, commendable. World and conflict building, commendable. I truly enjoyed the story and I hope to know more of what happens next</span>
  <span id="freeText6856227003706250577" style="display:none">This book was amazing! The writing style improved and I began to closely relate more with Hunter, who's now a teenager. I really enjoyed witnessing how Hunter becomes more and more conscious of his surrounding. His character development was exceptional and even I am learning from his experiences and from the way he faces the not-so-normal challenges around him. Plot wise, commendable. World and conflict building, commendable. I truly enjoyed the story and I hope to know more of what happens next! <br /><br />4.5 ⭐<br /><br />Thanks to BookTasters for recommending this book to me and to Dr. Brown for providing me a free copy of the book in exchange for an honest review.</span>
